headline: Exelon to Announce First Quarter Results on May 1
summary: CHICAGO, March 28, 2025--Exelon (Nasdaq: EXC) will hold its first quarter 2025 earnings conference call at 9:00 a.m. CT/10:00 a.m. ET on Thursday, May 1. The conference call will be led by Exelon President and CEO, Calvin Butler, and Exelon Executive Vice President and CFO, Jeanne Jones.
